'''Byss Mages''' were [[Dark side adept/Legends|Dark Side Adepts]] trained secretly on [[Byss/Legends|Byss]]. [[Arden Lyn]] participated in their training. These adepts helped [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] to create various organic experiments in his hidden facility.

